caption.title: GO annotations related to genes suppressed by PA-X.
caption.p: Enrichment analysis using GO Biological Process 2017b database of the 156 DEGs obtained from Fig 3B shows the pathways in which DEGs were suppressed by PA-X following virus infection. The ranking was based on the combined score, which was calculated from ln(P-value) Ã— Z-score (Enrichr).
